  "title": "Project Sales Coordinator (Technical Sales Coordinator)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Basic $2600 - $3200 + Variable Bonus</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working location: Tuas</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working days: Monday to Friday</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: 8am to 5pm</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Support, provide administrative support and manage daily sales operation and sales team</strong></li>\n  <li>Attend to calls and enquiries, process customer order, planning, scheduling and liaise with customer for order delivery</li>\n  <li><strong>Support project department in documentation preparation, filing, recording and updating</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Handle quotation and knowledgeable in purchase order, delivery order, sales order and invoicing</strong></li>\n  <li>Assists in preparation and submission of relevant report and documents for tender</li>\n  <li><strong>Vendor sourcing and procurement</strong></li>\n  <li>Stock monitoring and recording</li>\n  <li>Monitor shipment of order</li>\n  <li>ISO preparation &amp; filing</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with internal team to facilitate smooth process</li>\n  <li>Conduct sites visit where require</li>\n  <li>Any other ad hoc duties as assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess minimum Nitec and/or Diploma or related field</li>\n  <li><strong>Must for AutoCAD</strong> and Microsoft office applications</li>\n  <li>Prior experience in AutoCAD of Mechanical Engineering</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
